"title": "3296: Holy Spirit, work in the world",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3296",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit, active in the created world, works to show the futility and sinfulness of life without God, and brings a conviction of the presence of God, his righteousness and coming judgment.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit is active in the created world</h2>\n<h3>In creation itself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:4\">JOB 33:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:6\">PSA 33:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:2\">GEN 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:13\">JOB 26:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:30\">PSA 104:30</a></p>\n<h3>In ordering the natural world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:11-Isa34:17\">ISA 34:11–34:17</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit is present everywhere in the world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:7\">PSA 139:7</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The unbelieving world will not recognise the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:17\">JHN 14:17</a></strong> <em>John uses “the world” to describe those who live apart from God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit testifies to the truth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:16\">ROM 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:11-1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:11–2:14</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit convicts the world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:7-John16:11\">JHN 16:7–16:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:24-1Cor14:25\">1CO 14:24–14:25</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit empowers the church to serve the world in mission</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26-John15:27\">JHN 15:26–15:27</a></p>",
